                <head>Senator Hunter Out at Last</head>
                <origin>Charlottesville Jeffersonian</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Letter from Senator Hunter to Hon. S.F. Leake reveals that Hunter supports
                    Buchanan. Affirms convention system for establishing constitution in
                Kansas.</summary>
            </div>
