                        <ln>Young</ln>
                        <pf>Dr.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Dr. Young, who owns new Drug Store, has made numerous donations of food,
                    spices, and other goods to the newspaper.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>Horrible Occurance</head>
                <origin/>
