                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Gearhart</ln>
                        <pf>Jackson</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Six year-old daughter of Jackson Gearhart burnt to death when clothes
                    caught fire at fireplace while she played with other children.</summary>
            </div>
